{"tid":673131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有朋友去左同自己嘅「神」傾計 可唔可信？","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T14:42:08.000Z","uid":159228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c86e56aff8efb19e9b5102bfc65796901a02d237","tid":673131,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"話說我有個朋友好迷占卜呢樣野 <br />\n最近佢就揾左一間新嘅占卜店<br />\n間店好神秘 平時唔會開 只有你約佢佢先會開 <br />\n咁今日我朋友就去左 <br />\n然後個店主就話佢地唔係占卜<br />\n而係一個「訊息傳遞者 」<br />\n可以同守護你嘅「神」溝通<br />\n於是我朋友就比左千幾蚊去「溝通」<br />\n佢仲話好準 問一個問題 個神就可以答晒所有野 <br />\n好清楚自己嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n我朋友同返我講 話呢個叫「阿卡西紀錄」<br />\n我有點半信半疑<br />\n信係因為世界咁大乜都有可能<br />\n如果係真都唔出奇 <br />\n但唔信嘅係 點解個店主可以識同神溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位ching 點睇"},{"pid":"26ec316a474f503c44d9f079e14106338c416f00","tid":673131,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"青山咩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c661abf75f357a65e377dca81361a3648a8fcf8","tid":673131,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26ec316a474f503c44d9f079e14106338c416f00","tid":673131,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"青山咩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比你講一講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......."}]}